{"tid":1336613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解要全力支持記者？點解要「吹捧」？","createTime":"2019-07-21T04:44:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T07:32:26.000Z","uid":170051,"like":76,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6a94a23224db9527cc08befe398cfcc69e6c578b","tid":1336613,"uid":170051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T04:44:28.000Z","msg":"睇到有個post話<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好吹捧記者</span>，但居然有近2000正皮，<span style=\"color: red;\">證明真係好容易俾人帶風向</span>。<br />\n<br />\n大家諗一諗，我地<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">讚揚記者工作專業</span></span>有咩問題？即使記者報導只係中立，係呢個社會度<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">堅持呢個原則</span></span>已經好難，我地想讚揚佢地工作都唔得？何來「吹捧」之說？點解要用呢啲咁<span style=\"color: red;\">刻意煽情既說法</span>。<br />\n<br />\n記者係作為記者之前之後，佢地都有唔同既<span style=\"color: red;\">social role</span>，就好似警犬都係市民一樣，只不過佢地忘記左。<span style=\"color: red;\">根本冇所謂專業就完全不偏不倚既說法</span>。記者作為<span style=\"color: red;\">第四權</span>，事實係<span style=\"color: red;\">好多都被紅色資本收買，咁你係咪相信文匯大公不偏不倚？</span>而記者呢個角色可以如實反映事實已經幫左示威者唔少。因為你一個普通人同一個記者、傳媒去報告件事既影響力係完全唔同。<br />\n<br />\n再講，第四權既佢地有<span style=\"color: red;\">監察政府、警犬執法既權利，佢地日曬雨淋咁行使佢地既監察權，去還原事實真相，你估記者又唔係人？而且記者係度確實係可以令警犬相對低調啲</span>。無論記者立場係點，事實<span style=\"color: red;\">佢地既存在係好重要</span>。因為係呢個政權下面<span style=\"color: red;\">已經冇其他代公眾發聲既途徑</span>，不偏不倚既佢地係最後既大眾傳媒，咁都唔可以支持、讚揚下佢地？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">支持記者</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化、不割蓆、不篤灰<br />\n<br />\n3點見</span></span>"},{"pid":"0946339b1069ec81ed601b344699daaee25f6d48","tid":1336613,"uid":56052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T04:51:24.000Z","msg":"[突發] 一個和理非唔會散嘅方法 --- 基督之盾<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1336397\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1336397</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n一齊做盾，大家幫推"},{"pid":"9c93cadd448a306f73272c9703f1de7429a31bc9","tid":1336613,"uid":170051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T05:10:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"67cab0c9b448a5aef9bee5abaca0e7d446998b36","tid":1336613,"uid":170051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T05:10:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c573fc9248eed01edfdbf10add07a1f7e04198c","tid":1336613,"uid":170051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T05:10:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5401184a5a7cbeeab1ef377406f360048f5d2a1b","tid":1336613,"uid":170051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T05:10:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9c8017f97b520c46d90d1afc1f89764bf13bac9","tid":1336613,"uid":170051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T05:10:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"49181cadd545cfecd7451c51dc0f1f42bb69722a","tid":1336613,"uid":170051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T05:11:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b22041cc84f6e55e2ffc2013a41daa008ce26b53","tid":1336613,"uid":170051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T05:11:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"926a35db06f5a1d2d1618d8fc64d1bee6f32435b","tid":1336613,"uid":65858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T05:11:20.000Z","msg":"推呢個"},{"pid":"e014228f6f29d21f83a12ab96beb7d084deabf3b","tid":1336613,"uid":50414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T05:11:34.000Z","msg":"岩呀"},{"pid":"50d6ddd5845efe43579f229c09b3b5bc07e1c7c5","tid":1336613,"uid":170051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T05:11:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a97c4dfc0c0ba52c97add61da879df2abc52723","tid":1336613,"uid":170051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T05:11:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8bf994d83e182803ae78efccc8aa26d113ea404f","tid":1336613,"uid":170051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T05:12:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"07901ac820ae49d9a3